。作品共分为163集短剧（1940-2005），5部TV版（1975-2014），10部电影版（1992-2013）。\r\n汉纳-巴伯拉/米高梅动画时期制作114集（1940-1957），期间获得了7次奥斯卡最佳动画短片奖；\r\nGene Deitch/Rembrandt Films cartoons时期制作13集（1961-1962）；\r\n查克·琼斯/Sib Tower 12 cartoons时期制作34集（1963-1967）；\r\n汉纳-巴伯拉/透纳娱乐时期制作1集The Mansion Cat（2001）；\r\n华纳动画时期制作1集The Karate Guard（2005）；\r\n以上为163集短剧作品。\r\n1992制作了首部电影版作品Tom and Jerry: The Movie。\r\n2014年推出新TV版动画。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "16637150": {"data": {"tag_id": 16637150, "tag_name": "鬼畜星探企划", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1600339256, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "3390": {"data": {"tag_id": 3390, "tag_name": "校园", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "499": {"data": {"tag_id": 499, "tag_name": "音乐", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "9724": {"data": {"tag_id": 9724, "tag_name": "毕业", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/0d7de1d0f524268381c78a3461ed189b8e110300.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "也许是期盼着毕业的懵懂少年,也许是早已离开校园的&quot;哥哥姐姐&quot;。不管刚刚经历过什么,不管怎样的未来在等待着你,毕业,永远是人生永恒的记忆。希望那些将要毕业和不将要毕业的同学朋友们能珍惜现在所被给予的一切;希望那些早已走出校园的大家永远不要忘记毕业那一刻的回忆!", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_